{
  "stem": "25591.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She succeeded in making him a household word, and she failed in freeing him-- liberating him, because we are both convinced he was alive when my wife started the work.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I am immensely grateful that I could introduce legislation, which was my first piece of legislation, making him an honorary citizen.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We now have a statue in the capital that my wife arranged, and I passed the legislation.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We have the postage stamp coming up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He will be, for generations, an inspiration of what the code of conduct of human beings needs to be, that we are our brothers' and sisters' keepers.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I wasn't a child.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was 16.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was a very mature, very old 16.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we were very conscious of the fact that we were living in this house, because through Wallenberg, this house was under-- theoretically-- the protection of the Royal Swedish government.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were aware of the fact that there were scores of such houses, thousands and thousands of people, who were not deported to Auschwitz because of this man and what this man did.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And for a young boy-- 16-year-old boy-- who had given up all hope of surviving the war, as the year 1944 moved on, the opportunity of helping in a-- in a tiny, modest way, this incredible work that he was doing was-- it-- it gave meaning to what I thought was the last year of my life.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember him as a very serious person.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember him as a person with a tremendous amount of personal presence with an authority.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember him as someone I would have followed in any direction, because I-- I sensed that he was motivated by the finest of instincts.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
